</code></pre> to add a custom coupon or a discount code to the results page and apply it to all the products. Note, that this coupon code needs to be first set up in your store.</p> <p>It is not currently possible to add discount coupons into your quiz built with RevenueHunt app for Magento.</p> <p>Your developer can, however, add a discount code to the results page using custom JavaScript code added to the Results page. </p> <p>Info</p> <p>Check out this article for more information on how to add custom JavaScript code to your results page.</p> <p>Example</p> <p>You can use this function </p> <p><pre><code>/* set specific discount code \*/
